  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "03bc6fe867e5c8615e51cc4aa8c145ba703d95c676fd3b1e231474fbaceb5d33": "[?], if you promise not to leave, can you help us work out what's happened here?",
    "047076a0629176919babe245728323548135bcffc4840ee34901dc7efc6f44ec": "It seems we're back to square one again, [?], unless you can think of anything else to investigate?",
    "a779f4a5022effae9fdf78a1dcf00c1e9a86657e62706ad883165536336b7ead": "That's right. She's the one who came here with Patzi. Like [?] here, both were uninvited.",
    "8957eca27863761d69036aab29b6f42ecc4897b6ebf4461747620692967d7221": "Alright, [?], just let us know when you want everyone gathered and we'll take them upstairs for you.",
    "7bebc05a4f66fd66b1f72cdfabe0f399aedd360c5b1ce779dd5eec39e69f0479": "You take the lead here, [?]. We'll be on hand to support you where needed.",
    "627e4b56462b008768a8aa39b734da317ef736d009303dbe5d63e4781acea645": "Perhaps you should make sure you've questioned everyone before making an accusation, [?].",
    "105359e9b15ad6ba04e408f093bf0d210160f5d7f5c067339c08ca239cc95e7b": "He makes a fair point, [?].",
    "d05d8025aaa06aa41b6975aa5ef401cf7bf6f4c43fb5fcbf709b1877b12194b7": "I suppose that is fair, [?], and lying isn't a crime on its own.",
    "e3e7bf48093390fe6ee85f14c0563ebf2f03f3c27734bf932ee4991950bdc800": "I think he's right, [?]. There's no real motive here.",
    "af047597bf0bf3e0098c2674a22f0bfcb4fc0421415b5ea66fc0d4d00533cd9b": "The pathway leads around the cliffs to the south. We'll see you at the theatre, [?].",
    "0d782c76e79d3af8e6584720863e90c22539164bca5eed34a251cc37433d3b68": "Ah, there you are, [?].",
    "ba9e2c4fcbf16c575317c06c9727558ee3224fac707d5f1ca04d3485d71b09a5": "The play is well underway and for all we know there's still a killer out there. I hope you have something for us, [?].",
    "e7d181e73e8bf8952b3324c91dd7c23d64ef149995c36e999abb20a4137af487": "Do you have new information that changes that, [?]?",
    "d9da05f189f64664421dd4aece717f20f527862617bada9f6ede12d5789149a1": "We're going to need more than that, [?].",
    "8d229b14551669cc1dd485b9b4621e007c2167f50651d79a8a69ac812f1c6e78": "Sounds like she might not be our killer then, [?].",
    "54ab55805fb47f35dab5a663ada0ee2a7f944363068a75b459868fe04aaa966a": "Of course it wasn't us! Stop messing around, [?]!",
    "efe489da87f03548938f23e4deda103ac32425cbc5e0345a7047715e23a7c50a": "Stop playing around, [?]! We have a killer to deal with!",
    "412f710097b9d358c8ff7e9a95e45a5da1a9ecb43ed480cd3f4461b51db11389": "Be quick, [?].",
    "a5ba7d11472fdcbd80d165a6afe5d3b2392d2f80cd23278f9e094ef9412d5357": "[?], you've done well. I'd like to apologise for our hasty arrest earlier. Your commitment to helping us has been commendable.",
    "5057e2d6353b2a7b92f1f199ad9e696c1c613f41d55d296398efb96141e0dbed": "You win some and you lose some I guess. All the best, [?]!"
  }
}